---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import BrandBranchesGrid from '../../components/BrandBranchesGrid.astro';
import { MAIN_PHONE, MAIN_PHONE_TEL } from '../../data/branches';

const title = "Maytag Refrigerator Repair | Southern California | French Door, Ice";
const description = "Maytag fridge repair across Southern California — French Door, side-by-side, ice maker module, 10-year compressor warranty. Whirlpool-owned. $89 diagnostic. (424) 325-0520.";
const canonical = "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/maytag-refrigerator-repair/";

const faqs = [
  {
    q: "Is Maytag still the \"dependability\" brand, and what does that mean for service?",
    a: "Maytag's \"Maytag Man\" dependability positioning has been a durable brand identity since the mid-20th century, and current-generation Maytag refrigerators carry that through with a 10-year limited parts warranty on the compressor (parts only, not labor) — longer than the typical 1-year parts-and-labor or 2-year manufacturer standard. Whirlpool Corporation acquired Maytag in 2006, and since then Maytag has operated as Whirlpool's durability-positioned sub-brand. Chassis platforms are shared with Whirlpool mainstream and KitchenAid premium — many service items cross-reference between these Whirlpool-family brands. For LA service, the 10-year compressor warranty is meaningful: if your Maytag is under 10 years old and the compressor fails, LG-equivalent parts coverage reduces your out-of-pocket cost substantially. We check Maytag warranty status by serial number before quoting major compressor repairs."
  },
  {
    q: "What Maytag refrigerator models are most common in LA?",
    a: "By volume, Maytag French Door MFI and MFF families dominate LA Maytag service — 25–28 cu ft capacity, ice + water dispenser, PowerCold Feature, adjustable shelving. Maytag side-by-side MSS and MSF families are second-most-common. Maytag top-freezer MET series shows up in rental-property and apartment-building installs alongside similar-tier Roper, Amana, and base-tier Whirlpool. Maytag counter-depth variants (MFI French Door counter-depth) land in kitchen-remodel applications. Maytag ice-maker-trim configurations (external ice + water through-the-door) are the common feature configuration; simpler factory ice-maker-in-freezer layouts appear on base-trim Maytag. PowerCold Feature (rapid-cooldown button for hot-food-in-fridge situations) is a Maytag-branded platform feature that's sometimes a service-path consideration."
  },
  {
    q: "How does the Maytag 10-year limited compressor warranty actually work?",
    a: "Maytag covers the compressor itself for 10 years — parts only, not labor, not other refrigeration components. Labor and ancillary parts (capacitors, start relays, control boards, fan motors, sealed-system components) become the owner's responsibility after the baseline 1-year parts-and-labor warranty period expires. Practical implication: if you're within 10 years of purchase and the compressor fails, Maytag covers the compressor part cost, but you pay labor ($400–$650) and any ancillary parts that need replacement as part of the repair. We verify Maytag warranty status by model and serial number through Whirlpool's service portal before quoting major compressor work — if the compressor is under coverage, total out-of-pocket drops significantly compared to a full out-of-warranty compressor swap ($900–$1,500). For units past 10 years, full post-warranty compressor replacement applies."
  },
  {
    q: "Maytag fridge not cooling — walk through what you'd check?",
    a: "Our Maytag no-cool diagnostic sequence matches the broader French-door and side-by-side pattern. In order: (1) condenser coil dust + clearance check — especially in warm LA kitchens where coil heat rejection is critical; clean $160–$260; (2) evaporator fan motor bearing — fan failure cools the freezer only (thermal mass) before fridge warms; swap $280–$440; (3) defrost heater + thermostat — ice buildup on evaporator blocks airflow; replacement $320–$480; (4) damper door — airflow regulator stuck closed between freezer and fridge; swap $240–$380; (5) main control board — affects temperature logic; $380–$580; (6) compressor start relay + run capacitor — swap $180–$280; (7) actual compressor mechanical failure — rare, but within 10-year warranty parts cost is covered; labor $400–$650 in that case, full post-warranty $900–$1,500. Our techs run the diagnostic in this order explicitly to avoid defaulting to compressor quotes before ruling out cheaper root causes."
  },
  {
    q: "Maytag PowerCold Feature button not doing anything — is it broken?",
    a: "PowerCold Feature is Maytag's rapid-cooldown function — push the button and the fridge runs the compressor at maximum for a set period (typically 15–24 hours) to quickly chill newly-added warm food or restore temperature after a door-left-open event. Common failure modes: (1) button unresponsive — control-panel membrane switch failed; fix is membrane or control panel replacement $220–$360; (2) button works but no rapid-cooldown — main control board logic fault; $380–$580 board swap; (3) feature activates but doesn't improve cooling — underlying refrigeration-cycle issue is the real problem; PowerCold can't compensate for a failing compressor or blocked evaporator. Diagnostic approach: verify underlying refrigeration is working at normal setpoint, then diagnose the PowerCold-specific electronics. PowerCold is a nice-to-have feature, not critical — many Maytag owners go years without using it and only notice it doesn't work during a needed rapid-cooldown event."
  },
  {
    q: "What does Maytag refrigerator repair cost in LA?",
    a: "Residential diagnostic is $89, waived when you authorize the repair. Common Maytag bands: condenser coil clean + diagnostic $160–$260; EveryDrop filter service $160–$260; door gasket (French Door) $220–$380; door gasket (side-by-side or top-freezer) $200–$340; ice-maker module $280–$440; water-inlet valve $240–$380; dispenser actuator $180–$280; evaporator fan motor $280–$440; condenser fan motor $260–$420; defrost heater + thermostat $320–$480; damper door $240–$380; main control board $380–$580; PowerCold control panel / membrane $220–$360; compressor start/run capacitor $180–$280; compressor labor (with 10-year parts coverage) $400–$650; compressor full replacement (post-warranty) $900–$1,500. Our dispatch verifies Maytag warranty status before major-repair quotes — the 10-year compressor parts coverage changes economics on many repair decisions."
  }
];

const schemaJsons = [
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "LocalBusiness",
    "@id": canonical + "#business",
    "name": "Same Day Appliance Repair — Maytag Refrigerator Service",
    "image": "https://samedayappliance.repair/images/same-day-appliance-repair.png",
    "url": canonical,
    "telephone": MAIN_PHONE_TEL,
    "priceRange": "$$",
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ]
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "Service",
    "serviceType": "Maytag Refrigerator Repair",
    "provider": { "@id": canonical + "#business" },
    "areaServed": [
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Los Angeles County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Orange County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Ventura County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "San Bernardino County" },
      { "@type": "AdministrativeArea", "name": "Riverside County" }
    ],
    "description": "Maytag refrigerator repair across Los Angeles — MFI / MFF French Door, MSS / MSF side-by-side, MET top-freezer. Whirlpool-owned dependability sub-brand since 2006. 10-year limited parts warranty on compressor. PowerCold Feature, EveryDrop filter system. $89 residential diagnostic waived with repair.",
    "offers": {
      "@type": "Offer",
      "priceSpecification": {
        "@type": "PriceSpecification",
        "price": "89.00",
        "priceCurrency": "USD",
        "description": "Residential diagnostic fee, waived with repair"
      }
    }
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "FAQPage",
    "mainEntity": faqs.map(f => ({ "@type": "Question", "name": f.q, "acceptedAnswer": { "@type": "Answer", "text": f.a } }))
  },
  {
    "@context": "https://schema.org",
    "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
    "itemListElement": [
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Brands", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Maytag", "item": "https://samedayappliance.repair/brands/maytag/" },
      { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 4, "name": "Maytag Refrigerator Repair", "item": canonical }
    ]
  }
];
---

<Layout title={title} description={description} canonical={canonical}>
  <Fragment slot="head-scripts">
    {schemaJsons.map((schema) => (
      <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} />
    ))}
  </Fragment>

  <div class="call-banner">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span>Maytag fridge service? Same-day across LA:</span>
      <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="phone-lg">{MAIN_PHONE}</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="hero"><div class="wrap">
          <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> › <a href="/brands/">Brands</a> › Maytag › Refrigerator Repair</div>
          <h1>Maytag Refrigerator Repair</h1>
          <p class="lede">
            Maytag is Whirlpool Corporation's dependability-positioned sub-brand — same corporate parent
            as Whirlpool, KitchenAid, Amana, JennAir, and the Roper nameplate, with chassis-shared
            platforms across most service items. Whirlpool acquired Maytag in 2006, and since then the
            Maytag refrigerator lineup has carried a durability-emphasis positioning anchored by the
            10-year limited parts warranty on the compressor — longer than the typical 1-year or 2-year
            manufacturer baseline. The \"Maytag Man\" brand identity has been continuous since the mid-20th
            century. Our LA Maytag service covers French Door (MFI, MFF), side-by-side (MSS, MSF), top-
            freezer (MET) across mass-market, rental-property, and mid-market households. Same-day
            dispatch, $89 residential diagnostic waived with the repair.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-cta">
            <a href={`tel:${MAIN_PHONE_TEL}`} class="btn btn-primary">Call {MAIN_PHONE}</a>
            <a href="#book" class="btn btn-ghost">Request a Visit</a>
          </div>
          <ul class="hero-facts">
            <li><b>Whirlpool-owned since 2006</b> — chassis-shared with Whirlpool-family brands</li>
            <li><b>10-year limited parts warranty on compressor</b> — we verify coverage before major-repair quotes</li>
            <li><b>PowerCold Feature service</b> — control panel + logic diagnostics</li>
            <li><b>$89 residential diagnostic</b> — waived when you authorize the repair</li>
          </ul>
        </div></section>

  <BrandBranchesGrid />

  <section class="trust-bar">
    <div class="wrap">
      <span>CSLB #1138898 · Insured</span>
      <span>Same-day in 5 SoCal counties</span>
      <span>Residential diagnostic $89 · waived with repair</span>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Maytag in LA — Whirlpool's dependability sub-brand</h2>
      <p>
        Maytag's brand identity — durability, reliability, the iconic lonely-repairman Maytag Man campaign
        — has been a fixture of US appliance marketing for decades. Whirlpool Corporation's 2006
        acquisition integrated Maytag into the broader Whirlpool Corporation portfolio (Whirlpool,
        KitchenAid, Maytag, Amana, JennAir, Roper). For refrigerators, Maytag's current-generation
        positioning centers on the 10-year limited parts warranty on the compressor — the longest
        mainstream-brand compressor parts coverage available — which our techs factor into repair-vs-
        replace diagnostic reasoning whenever a Maytag compressor failure is on the table.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our LA Maytag service territory spans mass-market and mid-market geographies: San Fernando Valley
        (Sherman Oaks, Van Nuys, Northridge, Woodland Hills), San Gabriel Valley (Pasadena, Alhambra,
        Arcadia, Monterey Park), South Bay (Torrance, Long Beach, Redondo Beach), Westside mid-market
        (Culver City, Mar Vista, Palms), and rental-property + property-management accounts across the
        broader LA basin. Maytag's dependability brand positioning plus Whirlpool-family parts inventory
        makes the brand a solid fit for property-management portfolios where long-service-life per-unit
        economics matter.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Maytag refrigerator failures our techs see most often in LA</h2>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Water-dispenser + ice-maker (EveryDrop filter)</h3>
        <p>
          Whirlpool-family EveryDrop filter system shared with Maytag. LA hard-water service pattern
          matches Whirlpool sibling brands. Filter + housing clean $160–$260; water-inlet valve $240–$380;
          ice-maker module $280–$440.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Fridge warm, freezer cold — evaporator fan or defrost</h3>
        <p>
          Standard French-door and side-by-side diagnostic pattern. Fan motor $280–$440; defrost heater +
          thermostat $320–$480; damper door $240–$380; control board $380–$580. Maytag chassis-sharing
          with Whirlpool means these service items cross-reference broadly.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>PowerCold Feature failures — membrane switch or board logic</h3>
        <p>
          Maytag-branded rapid-cooldown feature occasionally fails at the control panel level. Membrane
          switch or control panel replacement $220–$360; main control board logic fault $380–$580 swap.
          Verify underlying refrigeration is normal before diagnosing PowerCold-specific electronics.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Door gasket compression loss</h3>
        <p>
          6–10 year service item. French Door gasket $220–$380; side-by-side / top-freezer gasket $200–
          $340. Often preceded by frost buildup along door edge and continuous compressor cycling.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Compressor under 10-year limited parts warranty</h3>
        <p>
          Maytag's 10-year compressor parts coverage changes the economics when the compressor actually
          fails. Labor $400–$650 if parts are covered; full out-of-warranty replacement $900–$1,500. We
          verify warranty status by serial number before quoting major compressor work.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="fail-block">
        <h3>Start relay + capacitor on older units</h3>
        <p>
          Start relay / run capacitor swap $180–$280 at 8–12 years. Distinct from compressor mechanical
          failure — these are the typical \"compressor won't start\" or \"clicking then cycling off\" root
          causes that precede actual compressor replacement.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>Maytag refrigerator product lines we service</h2>
      <div class="model-grid">
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>MFI / MFF French Door</h3>
          <p>25–28 cu ft French Door with ice + water dispenser. Volume platform across LA mass-market
          and mid-market kitchens.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>MFI counter-depth</h3>
          <p>Counter-depth French Door variants for flush-to-cabinet kitchen remodels. Same feature set
          as standard-depth MFI with shallower profile.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>MSS / MSF side-by-side</h3>
          <p>Side-by-side with ice + water through-the-door dispenser. Adjustable shelving, PowerCold
          Feature on higher trim.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>MET top-freezer</h3>
          <p>Top-freezer Maytag for rental-property and apartment installs. Simplified architecture;
          dependability-focused positioning.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>PowerCold Feature + specialty</h3>
          <p>Rapid-cooldown feature on higher-trim models. Specialty Maytag configurations including
          compact apartment variants.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="model-card">
          <h3>EveryDrop filter + Whirlpool-platform parts</h3>
          <p>EveryDrop filter shared across Whirlpool-family. Platform parts accelerate first-visit repair
          on any Maytag service call.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Maytag warranty context — the 10-year parts coverage math</h2>
      <p>
        Maytag's 10-year limited parts warranty on the compressor is the longest mainstream-brand
        compressor parts coverage. What this means for service:
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>Year 1:</b> full warranty — parts and labor covered on most repairs (go through Maytag / Whirlpool
        customer service first).
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>Years 2–10:</b> compressor parts covered if the compressor fails. Labor and other parts
        (capacitors, relays, boards, fans) are owner responsibility. Practical implication: compressor
        replacement in this window costs $400–$650 labor instead of $900–$1,500 full replacement.
      </p>
      <p>
        <b>Year 10-plus:</b> post-warranty — full repair economics, repair-vs-replace math shifts depending
        on unit condition.
      </p>
      <p>
        Our dispatch verifies Maytag warranty coverage by serial number before quoting major compressor
        repairs. Sometimes the same fault that would cost $1,500 on a non-Maytag is $500 on a Maytag
        within coverage — genuinely meaningful economics.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>What Maytag refrigerator repair costs in LA</h2>
      <table class="price-table">
        <tr><th>Service</th><th>Typical Range</th><th>Notes</th></tr>
        <tr><td>Residential diagnostic</td><td>$89</td><td>Flat, waived if repair is authorized same visit</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Condenser coil clean + diagnostic</td><td>$160 – $260</td><td>Preventive service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>EveryDrop filter + housing clean</td><td>$160 – $260</td><td>Hard-water LA service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Door gasket (French Door)</td><td>$220 – $380</td><td>Two-door profile</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Door gasket (side-by-side / top-freezer)</td><td>$200 – $340</td><td>Single-door or split profile</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Ice-maker module</td><td>$280 – $440</td><td>Volume-platform service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Water-inlet valve</td><td>$240 – $380</td><td>Dispenser + ice path</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Evaporator fan motor</td><td>$280 – $440</td><td>Freezer section</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Condenser fan motor</td><td>$260 – $420</td><td>Rear-bottom</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Defrost heater + thermostat</td><td>$320 – $480</td><td>Defrost-cycle repair</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Damper door</td><td>$240 – $380</td><td>Airflow regulator</td></tr>
        <tr><td>PowerCold control panel / membrane</td><td>$220 – $360</td><td>Rapid-cooldown feature</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Main control board</td><td>$380 – $580</td><td>Electronic generations</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor start / run capacitor</td><td>$180 – $280</td><td>8–12 year service</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor labor (parts under 10-yr warranty)</td><td>$400 – $650</td><td>Warranty-verified</td></tr>
        <tr><td>Compressor full replacement (post-warranty)</td><td>$900 – $1,500</td><td>Year-10-plus units</td></tr>
      </table>
      <p class="small">
        Broader reference: <a href="/price-list/refrigerator-repair-cost/">refrigerator repair cost
        guide</a>. Whirlpool-family sibling brands:
        <a href="/brands/whirlpool-refrigerator-repair/">Whirlpool</a>,
        <a href="/brands/kitchenaid-refrigerator-repair/">KitchenAid</a>,
        <a href="/brands/amana-refrigerator-repair/">Amana</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h2>LA service areas — where our Maytag calls come from</h2>
      <div class="area-grid">
        <div>
          <h4>San Fernando Valley</h4>
          <p>Sherman Oaks · Van Nuys · Northridge · Woodland Hills · <a href="/encino/">Encino</a> · Reseda · Tarzana</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>San Gabriel Valley + Pasadena</h4>
          <p><a href="/pasadena/">Pasadena</a> · Alhambra · Monterey Park · Arcadia · San Gabriel · Rosemead</p>
        </div>
        <div>
