          <p>Culver City · Mar Vista · Palms · Westwood · <a href="/santa-monica/">Santa Monica</a></p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>East LA + multifamily</h4>
          <p>Boyle Heights · East Los Angeles · Lincoln Heights · El Sereno · Highland Park</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h4>Ventura + Orange County</h4>
          <p><a href="/thousand-oaks/">Thousand Oaks</a> · Simi Valley · <a href="/irvine/">Irvine</a> · Anaheim · Santa Ana</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Related Maytag and Whirlpool-family pages</h2>
      <ul class="related-links">
        <li><a href="/brands/whirlpool-refrigerator-repair/">Whirlpool refrigerator repair (parent) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/kitchenaid-refrigerator-repair/">KitchenAid refrigerator repair (premium sibling) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/amana-refrigerator-repair/">Amana refrigerator repair (value sibling) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/jennair-refrigerator-repair/">JennAir refrigerator repair →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/brands/roper-refrigerator-repair/">Roper refrigerator repair (budget sibling) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/services/refrigerator-repair/">Refrigerator repair (service hub) →</a></li>
        <li><a href="/price-list/refrigerator-repair-cost/">Refrigerator repair cost guide →</a></li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section alt">
    <div class="wrap narrow">
      <h2>Maytag refrigerator repair — frequently asked</h2>
      {faqs.map(f => (
